            <div><p style="margin:0 0 2px;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--label)">Briefing</p><p style="margin:0;font-size:13px;color:var(--label2)">The crew briefing note. Three phase tabs — Preflight, Enroute, Descent — organise the content for each phase of flight. Editable fields are shown in <span style="color:var(--tint)">tint colour with a dotted underline</span>.</p></div>
